---
title: Lemon Cheesecake Pots with Biscuit Crumb & Passionfruit Lemon Sauce | Serves 4+
description: Creamy and fruity, these lemon cheesecake pots are sure to be a crowd-pleaser! Assemble three layers of goodness: start with a sweet crumb, load up the citrusy cheesecake filling, then top with our lemon passionfruit sauce.
